question: Welches Vielfliegerprogramm hat die meisten Fluggesellschaften?
sparqlQald: SELECT ?uri WHERE { ?airline <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#type> <http://dbpedia.org/ontology/Airline> . ?airline <http://dbpedia.org/property/frequentFlyer> ?uri. } GROUP BY ?uri ORDER BY DESC(COUNT(DISTINCT ?airline)) OFFSET 0 LIMIT 1
sparql:
SELECT ?programmLabel (COUNT(DISTINCT ?fluggesellschaft) AS ?anzahlFluggesellschaften)
WHERE {
  ?programm rdf:type dbo:AirlineMilesProgram .
  ?programm dbo:wikiPageID ?programmID .
  ?fluggesellschaft dbo:airlineMilesProgram ?programm .
}
GROUP BY ?programmLabel
ORDER BY DESC(?anzahlFluggesellschaften)
LIMIT 1

question: Welche deutschen Städte haben mehr als 250000 Einwohner?
sparqlQald: SELECT DISTINCT ?uri WHERE { { ?uri a <http://dbpedia.org/ontology/City> } UNION { ?uri a <http://dbpedia.org/ontology/Town> } ?uri <http://dbpedia.org/ontology/country> <http://dbpedia.org/resource/Germany> ; <http://dbpedia.org/ontology/populationTotal> ?population FILTER ( ?population > 250000 ) }
sparql:
PREFIX rdf: <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#>
PREFIX dbo: <http://dbpedia.org/ontology/>
PREFIX dbp: <http://dbpedia.org/property/>
PREFIX rdfs: <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#>

SELECT ?stadt
WHERE {
  ?stadt rdf:type dbo:City ;
         dbp:populationTotal ?einwohner .
  FILTER(langMatches(lang(?stadt), "de")) .
  FILTER(?einwohner > 250000) .
}

PREFIX dbo: <http://dbpedia.org/ontology/>

PREFIX dbc: <http://dbpedia.org/resource/Category:>
PREFIX rdfs: <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#>

question: Welcher Dichter hat die meisten Bücher geschrieben?
sparqlQald: SELECT DISTINCT ?uri WHERE { ?uri <http://dbpedia.org/ontology/occupation> <http://dbpedia.org/resource/Poet> . ?x <http://dbpedia.org/ontology/author> ?uri . ?x <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#type> <http://dbpedia.org/ontology/Book> . } ORDER BY DESC(COUNT(?x)) OFFSET 0 LIMIT 1
sparql:
PREFIX rdf: <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#>
PREFIX dbo: <http://dbpedia.org/ontology/>
PREFIX foaf:<http://xmlns.com/foaf/0.1/>
SELECT DISTINCT ?author ?name (COUNT(?book) AS ?numBooks)
WHERE {
  ?author rdf:type dbo:Writer .
  ?author foaf:name ?name .
  ?book rdf:type dbo:Book .
  ?book dbo:author ?author .
}
GROUP BY ?author ?name
ORDER BY DESC(?numBooks)
LIMIT 1

question: Welche Töchter von britischen Grafen starben an den gleichen Orten, an denen sie geboren wurden?
sparqlQald: PREFIX dbo: <http://dbpedia.org/ontology/> PREFIX yago: <http://dbpedia.org/class/yago/> PREFIX rdf: <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#> SELECT DISTINCT ?uri WHERE { ?uri rdf:type yago:WikicatDaughtersOfBritishEarls ; dbo:birthPlace ?x ; dbo:deathPlace ?y FILTER ( ?x = ?y ) }
sparql:
PREFIX dbo: <http://dbpedia.org/ontology/>
PREFIX dbp: <http://dbpedia.org/property/>
PREFIX dbr: <http://dbpedia.org/resource/>
SELECT ?name ?birthPlace ?deathPlace
WHERE {
  ?person dbo:parent [dbo:father ?father; dbo:mother ?mother].
  ?person dbo:birthPlace ?birthPlace.
  ?person dbo:deathPlace ?deathPlace.
  ?father dbp:title ?title.
  FILTER (regex(?title, "Earl", "i") || regex(?title, "Countess", "i")).
  FILTER (?birthPlace = ?deathPlace).
  ?person dbo:birthDate ?birthDate.
  ?person dbo:deathDate ?deathDate.

}

question: Wo fängt Piccadilly an?
sparqlQald: SELECT DISTINCT ?uri WHERE { ?uri <http://dbpedia.org/ontology/routeStart> <http://dbpedia.org/resource/Piccadilly> }
sparql:
PREFIX dbo: <http://dbpedia.org/ontology/>
PREFIX geo: <http://www.w3.org/2003/01/geo/wgs84_pos#>

SELECT ?start
WHERE {
  ?subject dbo:wikiPageWikiLink <http://dbpedia.org/resource/Piccadilly_Circus> .
  ?subject geo:lat ?lat .
  ?subject geo:long ?long .
  FILTER (?lat >= 51.509 && ?lat <= 51.511 && ?long >= -0.139 && ?long <= -0.137)
  ?start geo:lat ?startLat .
  ?start geo:long ?startLong .
  FILTER (?startLat >= ?lat && ?startLat <= ?lat+0.001 && ?startLong >= ?long && ?startLong <= ?long+0.001)
}
